{"tid":409962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【咪俾錢中介】夫被騙百五萬自縊死 妻終日恐懼：我都好想死","createTime":"2017-09-22T13:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T09:13:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f1e186b762b125cb67b95246972b04ebb2cbb6","tid":409962,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:21:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zfazuHksS0E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzfazuHksS0E&d=8byKljnyTFao98beCOqd5TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=ecd04c20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zfazuHksS0E</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170921/large/1505970198_0f22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170921%2Flarge%2F1505970198_0f22.jpg&h=5796d6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吸血中介財務詐騙情況猖獗，前年十二月一名印刷廠東主疑因財困，透過中介財務借取150萬，卻疑似誤墮貸款騙局，死者將物業作抵押後，不但收不到貸款，更因無力償還天文數字的債項而選擇在廠房內上吊自殺，遺下妻兒孤苦無依。 <br />\n<br />\n死者吳鎮華逝世至今近兩年，丈夫遺下的問題仍未解決，財務公司向她窮追猛打，生活拮据，遺孀面對隨時被收樓的官司感前路茫茫，更曾有輕生之意。她哭訴香港是犯罪者天堂，丈夫被騙去150萬元全是顧問費，質疑警方為何無翻查銀行閉路電視查案，死者是由誰陪同往銀行提款，她力斥犯罪份子為何仍能消遙法外，助長他們氣焰繼續害人。 <br />\n<br />\n每日返家看到信箱，不期然產生了很大壓力，她害怕再次接獲律師信和追數信。 <br />\n<br />\n「我都好想去似佢咁死咗一走了之，佢走咗，咩都唔知道，點解佢哋依家仲要逼人上絕路，就算佢死咗都解決唔到問題，人哋都唔會放過他，留下爛攤子，點解咁不負責任？！太自私了。」她最擔心現在死無對證，不利打官司，倘若未來遭強行收樓，她幽幽地說：「有可能再損失多一條人命」。 <br />\n<br />\n這夜，她站在化寶盤一旁，燒衣紙給丈夫，喃喃自語，叮嚀丈夫做鬼也不要放過害他的人，誓要找壞人報仇，言談間充滿着仇恨。 <br />\n<br />\n為免終日胡思亂想，年初開始經營小食店，索性以工作來忘記悲傷，獨力撐起一家三口的開支，也要苦撐下去，因為子女是她唯一生存動力，面對崎嶇前路，唯有見步行步。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170922/2_550027_0/-%E5%92%AA%E4%BF%BE%E9%8C%A2%E4%B8%AD%E4%BB%8B-%E5%A4%AB%E8%A2%AB%E9%A8%99%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%94%E8%90%AC%E8%87%AA%E7%B8%8A%E6%AD%BB-%E5%A6%BB%E7%B5%82%E6%97%A5%E6%81%90%E6%87%BC-%E6%88%91%E9%83%BD%E5%A5%BD%E6%83%B3%E6%AD%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170922%2F2_550027_0%2F-%25E5%2592%25AA%25E4%25BF%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BB%258B-%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25A8%2599%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%2594%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25B8%258A%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2587%25BC-%25E6%2588%2591%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%25AD%25BB&d=8byKljnyTFao98beCOqd5TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=10ca7bc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170922%2F2_550027_0%2F-%25E5%2592%25AA%25E4%25BF%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BB%258B-%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25A8%2599%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%2594%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25B8%258A%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2587%25BC-%25E6%2588%2591%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%25AD%25BB&h=5f77e18e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170922/2_550027_0/-%E5%92%AA%E4%BF%BE%E9%8C%A2%E4%B8%AD%E4%BB%8B-%E5%A4%AB%E8%A2%AB%E9%A8%99%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%94%E8%90%AC%E8%87%AA%E7%B8%8A%E6%AD%BB-%E5%A6%BB%E7%B5%82%E6%97%A5%E6%81%90%E6%87%BC-%E6%88%91%E9%83%BD%E5%A5%BD%E6%83%B3%E6%AD%BB</a>"},{"pid":"ecbf6afbb64874c346907007ceb9a38eb4177ff5","tid":409962,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe5ac00fb650e5dc48159e0353045c3e7a993de","tid":409962,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f03a1ae9535e693054dfd96d30e26f4cb037b7a","tid":409962,"uid":2436,"like":2,"disli